variant.summary:
This histogram measures the time step 5 took. It is emitted
                 at most once per the omnibox's request for bookmark matches;
                 it won't be emitted if step 3 matched no nodes.

This histogram measures the time step 4 took. It is emitted
                 at most once per the omnibox's request for bookmark matches;
