histogram.summary:
The size of TitledUrlIndex at startup. Its indexes can grow or shrink after startup as users edit bookmarks. But this is recorded only once at startup and estimates index size across users, unbiased by users who make more edits.
TitledUrlIndex has 2 index, 1 mapping each term in bookmark titles and URLs to a set of the containing bookmarks. The other mapping the set of path terms to the count of occurrences in bookmark paths.
{IndexSlice}
